---
title: Moroccan-Style Cannellini Bean Stew with Veggies & Tortilla Flatbreads
description: Inspired by 'harira', a traditional North African soup brimming with legumes, veggies and fresh herbs, this is no
humble stew! Simmer all the goodness with creamy coconut milk and our chermoula spice blend, and scoop it up
with golden, crispy flatbreads, straight from the oven.
